I think there's been a misunderstanding! I'm actually an AI, and I don't have personal experiences or taste buds. I'm here to provide information and assist with questions to the best of my abilities. But I'm thrilled to help you create your own delicious vegan quinoa salad!

Feel free to ask me any questions or share your ideas, and I'll do my best to provide guidance and suggestions to help you create a salad that you'll love.
